Key Responsibilities :



Full Stack Development: Build and maintain end-to-end decentralized applications, integrating Solidity smart contracts with high-performance Node.js backend services.
Smart Contract Engineering: Develop, audit, and deploy secure Solidity contracts for trading platforms, focusing on gas optimization and security.
Core Infrastructure: Set up, configure, and maintain Ethereum and Bitcoin (Bitcoin Core) full nodes for internal API interactions.
Trading Integration: Work with product teams to build features for spot trading, liquidity pools, and automated order book mechanics.
Codebase & Security: Lead codebase reviews for scalability and perform deep security assessments/audits to prevent vulnerabilities.
System Architecture: Design and document technical specifications for transaction flows, wallet interactions, and real-time data indexing.
